data.description: Step into luxurious country living with this magnificently updated 3,528 sq ft home, perfectly situated on 2 acres of beautifully landscaped property. This home features 4 spacious bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms, including a lavish primary suite on the main floor. Two additional bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms are also conveniently located on the main level, ensuring ample space for family and guests alike.The heart of the home has been transformed with a stunning farmhouse-themed redesign. As you step inside, be captivated by the bespoke farmhouse design, starting with the striking herringbone brick entry that seamlessly flows into the kitchen as a stylish backsplash. The culinary spaces are a masterpiece of form and function, boasting new, sleek cabinetry and pristine countertops. The bathrooms echo this theme of refined modernity, fully remodeled to include walk-in tile showers.The home's infrastructure includes a new architectural roof, windows, and HVAC system, ensuring years of comfort and efficiency. Fresh vinyl plank flooring and plush carpeting in the bedrooms complement the new trim and paint, rounding out the extensive remodel.Additional luxuries include a central vacuum system for effortless cleaning, a dedicated office for privacy and productivity, and a serene outdoor setting featuring a dog run, raised garden beds, and fruit trees. For the enthusiast or hobbyist, a massive 40ft x 60ft shop, matched in style to the main home, offers extensive space for projects and storage. The entire estate is fully irrigated, presenting lush views and a tranquil setting framed by the picturesque backdrop of Mount Adams.This property is a true gem, offering both the charm of the countryside and the conveniences of modern living. Contact your favorite realtor today for your private showing.
